-01" /><published>2026-04-01T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-04-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/04/01/Post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/04/01/Post.html"><![CDATA[<p>You have an ambitious nature and may make a name for yourself.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[You have an ambitious nature and may make a name for yourself.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2026-03-31</title><link href="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/31/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-31" /><published>2026-03-31T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-31T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/31/Post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/31/Post.html"><![CDATA[<p>You may be infinitely smaller than some things, but you’re infinitelylarger than others.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[You may be infinitely smaller than some things, but you’re infinitelylarger than others.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2026-03-30</title><link href="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/30/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-30" /><published>2026-03-30T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-30T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/30/Post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/30/Post.html"><![CDATA[<p>Your talents will be recognized and suitably rewarded.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Your talents will be recognized and suitably rewarded.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2026-03-29</title><link href="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/29/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-29" /><published>2026-03-29T00:00:00+00:00<